## @file
#
# This package provides libraries implementing the lower layers of the TPM2
# software stack appropriate for use in UEFI. Currently this includes the
# type marshaling API, the system API and a TCTI specific to UEFI built on
# top of the TCG2 protocol. A number of example UEFI applications are
# provided as well to demonstrate use of these libraries.
